        "class": "ital",
        "text": "mite",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Thus Becon says, “let us with the poor widow of the gospel at the least give ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "two minutes",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and God will surely approve and accept our good will.” The ",
        "children": []
